    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in mint condition \u2014 the absolute best you'll find on the used market. The exterior is essentially flawless, with no scratches, dents, or paint imperfections to speak of. The interior is equally pristine, showing virtually no signs of wear on the seats, trim, dashboard, or carpeting. Under the hood, the engine runs perfectly and all mechanical systems are in top-notch shape. Every feature and function works exactly as intended, and the vehicle has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. Prospective buyers can expect a used car that feels and looks nearly indistinguishable from a new one \u2014 a truly rare find.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we want to give you a clear and honest picture of what to expect. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a decent shine and holds up nicely from a distance, though up close you may notice a few minor scratches and light scuffs consistent with normal everyday use. There are no major dents or structural concerns. The interior is clean and well-maintained, with seats showing only light wear and all controls and features functioning as intended. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, transmission shifts properly, and brakes feel solid. We've ensured routine maintenance is up to date. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been cared for, and it's priced fairly to reflect its true condition. A great choice for a buyer looking for a reliable daily driver without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project car or a solid parts vehicle? This might be exactly what you've been searching for! We'll be upfront with you \u2014 this car is in poor condition, showing significant wear both inside and out, and will require meaningful mechanical and cosmetic attention. That said, it's a real opportunity for the right buyer who loves a hands-on project or needs a parts source. Come take a look and see the potential for yourself!",
      "price": 5500.0,
