    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and we are proud to present one of the finest examples you will find on the market today. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 the paint retains a deep, lustrous shine with no visible scratches, dents, or blemishes of any kind. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, and all trim pieces, moldings, and glass are in perfect order. The interior is equally impressive: every surface is clean, unworn, and fresh-looking, with no stains, tears, or fading on the upholstery, dashboard, or carpeting. All electronics, controls, and features function exactly as intended \u2014 windows, mirrors, climate control, infotainment, and safety systems all operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs smoothly with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. The tires have excellent tread depth remaining, and the brakes are in top-notch condition. This is a turn-key vehicle that requires absolutely nothing \u2014 you can drive it away with complete confidence and peace of mind.",
      "price": 46000.0,
